  17 Apr 2005; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  files/1.9.3-sysfs-instead-of-lspci.patch:
  Improved /sys parser with higher yield, will also pick up PCI adapters and
  integrated video adapters. Unmasking.

  17 Apr 2005; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  files/1.9.3-sysfs-instead-of-lspci.patch:
  Update sysfs patch, avoid matching incorrect data in pci.ids. Still masked.

